{"tid":1829807,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【抗暴小店】黃店餐廳PayMe內近10萬元被凍結 滙豐：個人轉賬設限額","createTime":"2020-01-19T05:44:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-19T10:52:41.000Z","uid":130626,"like":13,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"d8471a8f6c9c65a54c8524dba3f1d484b34b5a8c","tid":1829807,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T05:44:55.000Z","msg":"黃店餐廳膳心小館早前在專頁發文，以「手足募集」為題，只要自覺是位有「良知」的香港人，即可隨時預約見工。不過，該店指，最近其PayMe內近10萬元被凍結，未能轉出至公司銀行戶口，暫未知原因。<br />\n<br />\n膳心小館在其專頁發文指，今年農曆年前推出蛋卷、角仔、盆菜、糕點等，為手足們提供就業機會，產品亦大賣，而不少客戶亦透過PayMe付款。其在專頁指，最近其PayMe戶口內共99931.8元被扣起，未悉原因。「我哋公司戶口一向用開payme都無問題。自開始賣賀年食品後，被傳媒兩度報導後，就被hold錢了。我哋都想係誤會。可惜，佢哋成個網頁，連電話都無。分行又話唔關佢哋事，信息佢哋又唔覆！」膳心小館稱已找到義務律師作出跟進，星期二交上法院。<br />\n<br />\n有網民在膳心小館的Facebook留言，認為可能是餐廳使用了個人帳戶，其轉入金額已達上限。<br />\n<br />\n滙豐發言人回覆《蘋果》時表示：「PayMe為個人對個人轉賬(P2P)而設，而基於安全考慮，PayMe設有儲值、增值及轉賬限額。如進行個人對商戶轉賬（P2M），商戶可選用 PayMe for Business，當中並沒有設立任何交易限額。」該行指已知悉事件，將聯絡該客戶作進一步跟進，並提供適當的個人對商戶轉賬(P2M)解決方案。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，曾有市民發現PayMe戶口內有資金遭「扣起」，原因是PayMe個人帳戶設每年10萬元轉賬限額，限度用盡後，其餘資金只能留在錢包，直至明年PayMe額度重設才可再轉賬至銀行。不過，去年3月推出的商用版「PayMe for Business」則不設轉賬上限，但每筆交易商戶須繳付1.5%的交易費用。<br />\n<br />\n去年本報曾報道，有市民驚覺PayMe錢包內有資金遭「扣起」，提不出來，一查之下才發現每年10萬元轉賬至自己銀行戶口的限度已用盡，其餘資金只能留在錢包。事實上，用戶轉賬至銀行爆額後，可將資金傳給有餘額的朋友，要求他們將資金傳回自己銀行賬戶，再將資金交還給事主；或是以直接消費方式，將資金使用；又或將PayMe錢包升級（只限滙豐銀行賬戶）。<br />\n<br />\n記者曾致電膳心小館，但電話已經關機。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200119/large/1579404937_4c08.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200119%2Flarge%2F1579404937_4c08.jpg&h=4d48a560&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200119/large/1579410347_b102.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200119%2Flarge%2F1579410347_b102.jpg&h=a037a8a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200119/HXTUJBYMMHIW2OVZJQWSLP3GWI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200119%2FHXTUJBYMMHIW2OVZJQWSLP3GWI%2F&d=hCh8nFxZocjAH0BHn0nK1BqcspSF5fyAY0%2FEGx5AO9c%3D&h=467ec461\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200119%2FHXTUJBYMMHIW2OVZJQWSLP3GWI%2F&h=c47adff1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200119/HXTUJBYMMHIW2OVZJQWSLP3GWI/</a>"},{"pid":"bb2b7cea5c9d30a37ed4fd68f479fce3bf2d8769","tid":1829807,"uid":156258,"like":39,"dislike":3,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T05:48:35.000Z","msg":"唔關黃藍事啦<br />\n9成都係唔想俾手續費用個人戶口啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31b745c83497c318893847145b649bb1cb87313f","tid":1829807,"uid":51469,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T05:50:11.000Z","msg":"做乜關機呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf3492510ab33b4703d511f95fd88eae99d2301c","tid":1829807,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T05:58:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">便衣警想屈西九影相學生搶槍</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1829251\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1829251</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u96ftcR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu96ftcR.jpg&h=75a42d90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">坐爆48都要7000蚊保釋<br />\n又屈搶槍 又私刑<br />\n無人講？</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zu76z34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzu76z34.jpg&h=9d03f884&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ED13C